  "content_blocks": [
    {
      "heading_context_raw": "PART 11: RESIDENTIAL RESERVE (RR) ZONE",
      "text": "No development permit shall be issued in a Residential Reserve (RR) Zone except for one or more"
    },
    {
      "heading_context_raw": "of the following uses:",
      "text": "unit; (RC-Aug 9/22;E-Sep 15/22)"
    },
    {
      "heading_context_raw": "ZONE REQUIREMENTS RR",
      "text": "In any Residential Reserve (RR) Zone no development permit shall be issued except in conformity"
    },
    {
      "heading_context_raw": "with the following requirements:",
      "text": "Minimum Lot Area ................................................................................................................ 5 acres Minimum Lot Frontage .........................................................................................................360 feet Minimum Front Yard ................................................................................................... 30 ft. setback Minimum Rear Yard ................................................................................................................. 50 ft. Minimum Side Yard ................................................................................................................... 8 ft. Maximum Height of Building ................................................................................................... 35 ft. Maximum Number of Dwelling Units on Lot (not including secondary or backyard suites) (NWCC-Mar 8/21;E-Mar 27/21) ................................................................1 Lot Coverage ....................................................................................................................... 10%"
    },
    {
      "heading_context_raw": "SPECIAL REQUIREMENTS - UNSERVICED LOTS",
      "text": "Notwithstanding anything else in this By-law, the minimum lot frontage for unserviced lots within as RR zone may be reduced to one hundred twenty (120) feet and the minimum lot area reduced"
    },
    {
      "heading_context_raw": "to one (1) acre where the following conditions are met:",
      "text": "a) the original parcel of land contains a dwelling which was constructed on or before October 9, 1991 by-law: and, b) the lot completely fronts on a street which was public on or before October 9,1991. Notwithstanding anything else in this By -law, for 700 Kearney Lake Road (PID 40648370), the minimum lot frontage is reduced to one hundred fifty (150) feet and the minimum lot area is reduced to two (2) acres. (RC-Apr 24/01;E-May 25/01)"
    }
  ],
